version_description:
[Add alarm] Send push-message at interval time
[Calendar] Can be modified in the past history
[D-Day] Easily check if you’ve been out for

- Backup / Restore is now available. (Dropbox login required)
Now move even if you have a new phone.

-Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
See the tips and write more convenient!

-You can change the swipe direction of plus minus!
Swipe in the desired direction! :-b

-The design is also slightly improved!
You should like it!

-We listen to your feedback
We'll reward you with a steady update!

-You can register the deadline for the day.
-You can change the alarm time. Off -> On time can be changed.
-After the update, the first app launch may be delayed. Please wait even if the first app launch is delayed.

New Feature !!
Settings - Calendar mode as default
- Fixed to be visible from last inactive data tracker.
Fixed an issue where inactive activity charts were pushed out in calendar mode.

-Changed DatePicker style in iOS14
-Tracker proportion adjustment

The long-awaited memo feature is released!!! lol
8 new fonts have been added together.
Developers who have been preparing for updates since dawn will now go take a nap.. (-.-)zZ
